## CORE ENTITIES

### Company

The customer organisation using MarketSense. Root of all multi-tenant data.

```
id, name, plan, createdAt, updatedAt
```

### User

A person belonging to a Company. Has a role within that company.

```
id, companyId, email, name, role (ADMIN | MEMBER), createdAt
```

### Competitor

A company being monitored. Belongs to a Company.

```
id, companyId, name, website, logoUrl, isActive, createdAt, updatedAt
```

### CompetitorPage

A specific URL being monitored for a Competitor.

```
id, competitorId, companyId, url, pageType, browserProfile,
lastScannedAt, isActive, createdAt
```

### ScanRun

One execution of TinyFish agents across a set of pages.
Manual or automated. Always created before firing any agents.

```
id, companyId, competitorId, triggeredBy, triggeredByUserId,
status, pageResults (JSON), newChangesCount,
startedAt, completedAt, externalRunId (for async runs)
```

### Change

A detected difference on a monitored page. Core intelligence unit.

```
id, companyId, competitorId, competitorPageId, scanRunId,
changeType, signalType, priority, title, summary,
rawExtracted (JSON), previousExtracted (JSON),
contentHash, isRead, isDismissed, actionCreated,
detectedAt, enrichedAt
```

### Insight

AI-generated PM briefing synthesised from a batch of Changes.

```
id, companyId, competitorId, changeIds (array),
title, briefing, recommendedActions (JSON),
signalType, priority, generatedAt
```

### ActionItem

A work item created from a Change or Insight, linked to an external tool.

```
id, companyId, changeId, insightId, userId,
tool (JIRA | LINEAR | ASANA | NOTION),
externalTicketId, externalTicketUrl, status,
title, description, priority, assigneeId,
createdAt, completedAt
```

### ComplianceAlert

A detected BSE/NSE circular or regulatory notice.

```
id, companyId, title, circularNumber, category,
publishedAt, sourceUrl, summary, isRead, detectedAt
```

### AutomationRule

A user-configured rule for auto-creating work items from signals.

```
id, companyId, userId, name, isEnabled,
triggerChangeType, triggerSignalType, triggerPriority,
actionTool, actionProject, actionPriority, actionAssigneeId,
notifySlackChannel, createdAt
```

