## DOMAIN VOCABULARY — USE THESE TERMS CONSISTENTLY

| Term        | Definition                                     | Never use instead                |
| ----------- | ---------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| scan        | One execution of TinyFish agents               | "scrape", "crawl", "fetch"       |
| change      | A detected difference on a monitored page      | "update", "alert", "event"       |
| insight     | AI-generated strategic PM briefing             | "report", "summary", "analysis"  |
| signal      | Strategic classification of a change           | "tag", "label", "category"       |
| goal        | Natural language instruction given to TinyFish | "prompt", "query", "instruction" |
| enrichment  | Gemini AI processing of raw extracted data     | "analysis", "processing"         |
| action item | Work item created and linked to Jira/Linear    | "ticket", "task", "issue"        |
| page        | A specific URL being monitored                 | "source", "target", "endpoint"   |
| run         | Synonym for scan — one ScanRun execution       | "job", "process", "execution"    |

