## PRICING TIERS — MarketSense PLANS

```typescript
export const MarketSensePlan = {
  STARTER: "starter", // 1 PM, 3 competitors, manual scans only
  GROWTH: "growth", // 3 PMs, 10 competitors, basic automation
  ENTERPRISE: "enterprise", // Unlimited, full automation, Jira/Linear, SSO
} as const;
```

Feature gating rules:

- Starter: no automation, no integrations, no compliance module
- Growth: automation enabled, Jira + Linear only, compliance add-on
- Enterprise: all integrations, compliance included, custom rules, API access

