## NAMING CONVENTIONS — MarketSense SPECIFIC

### Files

- `*.service.ts` — business logic (scan.service.ts, change-detection.service.ts)
- `*.repository.ts` — database queries (scan.repository.ts, competitor.repository.ts)
- `*.goal.ts` — TinyFish goal builders (pricing.goal.ts, jobs.goal.ts)
- `*.actions.ts` — Next.js Server Actions (scan.actions.ts)
- `*.types.ts` — domain types (scan.types.ts, change.types.ts)

### Variables

- `scanRun` not `scan_run` or `job`
- `competitorPage` not `page` or `source`
- `changeType` not `type` or `category`
- `signalType` not `signal` or `tag`
- `resultJson` not `result` or `data` (TinyFish specific)
- `companyId` always camelCase, always from session

### Functions

- `buildPricingGoal()` not `getPricingGoal()` or `pricingGoal()`
- `detectChanges()` not `findChanges()` or `checkChanges()`
- `enrichChange()` not `analyzeChange()` or `processChange()`
- `runCompetitorScan()` not `scanCompetitor()` or `startScan()`

