## WHAT MarketSense IS NOT

- NOT a generic web scraping tool — it is a PM intelligence platform
- NOT a security monitoring tool
- NOT a customer support tool — insights are for product strategy, not support
- NOT a real-time dashboard — scans are on-demand, not streaming live data
- NOT autonomous — PMs are always in control of what gets acted upon
